s added weekly  The VMI Archives contain more than 10 000 images in various formats  Included are individual and group photographs of cadets  alumni  faculty  VMI buildings  cadet life  and other areas of Institute history  We also have photographs associated with collections of personal papers  Featured Exhibit Earliest Cadet Photographs  1845 1862  Visit our Online Exhibits Home to browse additional galleries VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 